8'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/4811117117730277568'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240553220000#c4811117117730277568' title=''/><author><name>vvtone</name><uri>http://www.vvtone.com.cn</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月24日 下午2:07:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2313085833703665316</id><published>2009-04-24T12:43:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-24T12:43:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>楼上的同学，sizeof(PROTO)不是你所期望的效果。</title><content type='html'>楼上的同学，sizeof(PROTO)不是你所期望的效果。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/2313085833703665316'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/2313085833703665316'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240548180000#c2313085833703665316' title=''/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_itipB8vBZzQ/SY1isusKAfI/AAAAAAAAAGo/4YF360m0Yto/S220/Thinker_BlogSpot.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月24日 下午12:43:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-8965393771629392668</id><published>2009-04-24T09:28:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-24T09:28:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>:) 我觉得可不可以这样呢？&#xa;enum PROTO{  PROTO_HTTP,  PROTO_FTP...</title><content type='html'>:) 我觉得可不可以这样呢？&lt;br /&gt;enum PROTO{  PROTO_HTTP,  PROTO_FTP,  PROTO_SMTP,  PROTO_SSH};&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;int nCntProto[sizeof(PROTO)/sizeof(PROTO_HTTP)];&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;呵呵 不过 没有这样写过 不知道可不可行</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/8965393771629392668'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/8965393771629392668'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240536480000#c8965393771629392668' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月24日 上午9:28:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-818172114863130320</id><published>2009-04-24T08:51:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-24T08:51:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>哦，算错了，加上PROTO_NUM ，正好是4个，这个虽然是个很好的技巧，但是在也算有个小的问题，就...</title><content type='html'>哦，算错了，加上PROTO_NUM ，正好是4个，这个虽然是个很好的技巧，但是在也算有个小的问题，就是一般定义ENUM的时候，其他人的理解应该表示某个状态或者数值，但是这个PROTO_NUM却表示其他的意思，感觉有些不挨边的，不过任何事情没有完美的，也算是挺好的创意了。致敬。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/818172114863130320'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/818172114863130320'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240534260000#c818172114863130320' title=''/><author><name>vvtone</name><uri>http://www.vvtone.com.cn</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月24日 上午8:51:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2751432262610368120</id><published>2009-04-23T16:24:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-23T16:24:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>楼上的同学，默认情况下（不设定初始值），枚举值从0开始依次递增。</title><content type='html'>楼上的同学，默认情况下（不设定初始值），枚举值从0开始依次递增。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/2751432262610368120'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/2751432262610368120'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240475040000#c2751432262610368120' title=''/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_itipB8vBZzQ/SY1isusKAfI/AAAAAAAAAGo/4YF360m0Yto/S220/Thinker_BlogSpot.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月23日 下午4:24:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1837433192198801371</id><published>2009-04-23T16:14:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-23T16:14:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>另外还需要定义初始值吧，如PROTO_HTTP=1，另外就是各个枚举的数值必须是连续的，才可以</title><content type='html'>另外还需要定义初始值吧，如PROTO_HTTP=1，另外就是各个枚举的数值必须是连续的，才可以</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/1837433192198801371'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/1837433192198801371'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240474440000#c1837433192198801371' title=''/><author><name>vvtone</name><uri>http://www.vvtone.cm.cn</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月23日 下午4:14:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2988191292211695700</id><published>2009-04-21T19:30:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-21T19:30:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>C++ 应该这样用才好:&#xa;tr1::array&amp;lt;size_t, PROTO_NUM&amp;gt; a...</title><content type='html'>C++ 应该这样用才好:&lt;br /&gt;tr1::array&amp;lt;size_t, PROTO_NUM&amp;gt; ar = { ... };&lt;br /&gt;这样既有C的效率， 又有边界检查。&lt;br /&gt;而且size_t比int有更好的移植性。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/2988191292211695700'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/2988191292211695700'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240313400000#c2988191292211695700' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月21日 下午7:30:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6120380085767701104</id><published>2009-04-20T09:48:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-20T09:48:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>非常感谢楼上同学的认真仔细 :)</title><content type='html'>非常感谢楼上同学的认真仔细 :)</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/6120380085767701104'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/6120380085767701104'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240192080000#c6120380085767701104' title=''/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_itipB8vBZzQ/SY1isusKAfI/AAAAAAAAAGo/4YF360m0Yto/S220/Thinker_BlogSpot.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月20日 上午9:48:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6683470097750972811</id><published>2009-04-20T07:55:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-20T07:55:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>版本2：下面&#xa;&quot;第4个是SSH&quot;应该为&quot;第3个是SSH&quot;</title><content type='html'>版本2：下面&lt;br /&gt;&quot;第4个是SSH&quot;应该为&quot;第3个是SSH&quot;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/6683470097750972811'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/6683470097750972811'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240185300000#c6683470097750972811' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月20日 上午7:55:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6868719640050671332</id><published>2009-04-19T19:50:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-19T19:50:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>1楼的同学，&#xa;如果另外定义PROTO_NUM常量，代码会有冗余。一旦协议类型有变化但又忘记调整PRO...</title><content type='html'>1楼的同学，&lt;br /&gt;如果另外定义PROTO_NUM常量，代码会有冗余。一旦协议类型有变化但又忘记调整PROTO_NUM的值，无形中就引入了Bug。&lt;br /&gt;不过PROTO_NUM确实和其它枚举常量的类型不一致，这算是美中不足 :(</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/6868719640050671332'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/6868719640050671332'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240141800000#c6868719640050671332' title=''/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_itipB8vBZzQ/SY1isusKAfI/AAAAAAAAAGo/4YF360m0Yto/S220/Thinker_BlogSpot.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月19日 下午7:50:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6389855733233708984</id><published>2009-04-19T19:02:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-19T19:02:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>用枚举的好处是，编译器会帮你数出到底有多少个协议，这样就能自动确保一致性。</title><content type='html'>用枚举的好处是，编译器会帮你数出到底有多少个协议，这样就能自动确保一致性。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/6389855733233708984'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/6389855733233708984'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240138920000#c6389855733233708984' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月19日 下午7:02:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2122791691836668991</id><published>2009-04-19T11:40:00.000+08:00</published><updated>2009-04-19T11:40:00.000+08:00</updated><title type='text'>代码中出现很多magic number固然不好，但版本4的trick也未必全是优点。为了不引起误解，...</title><content type='html'>代码中出现很多magic number固然不好，但版本4的trick也未必全是优点。为了不引起误解，enum里应该放相同“类型”的元素，前面4个都是协议类型，突然冒出一个PROTO_NUM算什么事？&lt;br /&gt;紧跟着enum后声明#define PROTO_NUM 4不就很清晰吗？这里的4并不算是magic number，因为不妨碍理解。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/2122791691836668991'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1022729887606912193/comments/default/2122791691836668991'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html?showComment=1240112400000#c2122791691836668991' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/04/c-cxx-enum-idiom.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1022729887606912193' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1022729887606912193' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-357517073"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2009年4月19日 上午11:40:00"/></entry></feed>